Compile:
gcc -g -c test.c -I/usr/local/include/mysql/include
Link:
gcc -o test test.o -L/usr/local/include/mysql/lib -lmysqlclient

If the two steps goes to error,try the follow sentences:
ln -s /usr/local/include/mysql/lib/lmysqlclient.so /usr/lib 

Using C program Language to connect the MySQL Server,Failed to connect the server.This is the solution's location:
http://aiezu.com/article/mysql_php_connect_through_socket.html


